{"title":"浪淘沙","authors":["沈其震"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈其震"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜闻胡耀邦同志在民主党派座谈会上谈国内经济形势、清除精神污染和整党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医国在医人，要点精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容污染毁天真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片至诚倾肺腑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透辟清新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期共葆青春，濡沫相亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整风党自率先身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形势二千年大好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛世同臻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼胡耀邦同志访问日本胜利归来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访问七天中，一阵旋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从南到北兴冲冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入理入情谈友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气度恢宏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如日丽晴空，天下为公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同文同种喜相逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共策和平昭万代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永息兵戎。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}